Hey there! 👋 

I'm CJ - your new AI Customer Support Lead. Think of me as that tireless teammate who handles your support queue 24/7, turns angry customers into fans, and gives you back your evenings.

I'm built to autonomously resolve 60-80% of your support tickets while turning all that support data into actual growth insights. No more drowning in customer complaints or losing sleep over weekend escalations.

Is this our first time chatting? I want to make sure I give you the right experience - whether that's a quick tour of what I can do, or jumping right back into helping with your support operations.

Fair warning: I'm still in beta, so think of this as getting early access to your future support superhero. Ready to see what I can do with your store data?
